based on the Five Principles of Peaceful Coexistence -- have 
withstood the test of time and can be described as model 
relations. The existing contacts, friendship, and cooperation 
between the two countries will grow even stronger in the days to 
come. I wholeheartedly hope for Pakistan's progress and for the 
happiness and prosperity of its people. 
