<F P=102>  HK2503013794 Guangzhou Guangdong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 0400 GMT 16 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2503013794 </F>
<F P=104>  Guangzhou Guangdong People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yesterday morning, State Councillor Chen Junsheng 
stressed in a full meeting of the Guangdong delegation that 
Guangdong must concentrate its efforts on the issue of grain to 
ensure the acreage producing grain, increase grain output, and 
raise the self-support level of grain to guarantee the 
settlement of the issue of feeding Guangdong's people. 
  Chen Junsheng pointed out: The key to stabilizing grain 
production and increasing the self-support level of grain lies 
in stabilizing the acreage under grain. He said: Now there are 
too many development zones, and they have occupied a lot of good 
farmland. If the situation remains unchanged, grain output will 
drop. This situation must be changed very rapidly. 

