Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Hainan delegation to the second session of the 
Eighth National People's Congress [NPC] returned to Haikou by 
special plane at 1600 today. Receiving them at the Haikou 
airport were leading members of the provincial party committee, 
people's congress, government, and committee of the Chinese 
People's Political Consultative Conference including Wang 
Xiaofeng, Chen Yuyi, Xiao Xuchu, Wang Houhong, Dong Fanyuan, Liu 
