interviews by reporters. They briefed the reporters on the 
grand occasion of the second session of the Eighth National 
People's Congress, indicated that it was a session characterized 
by solidarity and seeking truth from facts, and would eventually 
play a role in promoting the deepening of reform, expanding 
opening up, and accelerating economic development in Hainan. 

