<H3> <TI>   Henan Industrial, Agricultural Output Increase </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK2703050794 Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 23 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2703050794 </F>
<F P=104>  Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] According to a briefing by a related department, 
in 1993, the fulfillment of Henan's major economic indices 
increased markedly from the previous year, for which the gross 
national product was 153 billion yuan, up by 15.7 percent, 
ranking seventh in China. The increase in grain output was 
36.39 million tons, ranking third in the country. Gross 
industrial output value increased by 29.1 percent from the 
previous year, for which the gross industrial output value of 
enterprises at and above the township level was 130.035 billion 
yuan, ranking 14th. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

